# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Mundaring

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 144 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Mundaring, of which 26 are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following 26 state registered places within the Shire of Mundaring:
